Fri, Oct 2, 2015, 13:45 BST - UK Markets close in 2 hrs 45 mins MURPHY OIL SCHEDULES EARNINGS CONFERENCE CALL Press Release : Murphy Oil Corp â€“ 14 minutes ago 23.65 -0.55 
EL DORADO, Arkansas, October 2, 2015 - Murphy Oil Corporation ( MUR ) has scheduled its earnings conference call at 12:00 p.m. Central Daylight Time (CDT), on Thursday, October 29, 2015, to review third quarter 2015 earnings, which will be announced after market close on Wednesday, October 28, 2015. 
Interested parties may participate by dialing 1-888-208-1617 and referencing reservation number 107766 . The live audio webcast and presentation materials can be accessed through the Investor Relations section of Murphy Oil`s website at http://ir.murphyoilcorp.com . 
A recording of the earnings conference call will be available through Thursday, November 12, 2015, by dialing 1-888-203-1112 and referencing reservation number 107766. 
For further information contact Kelly Whitley, Vice President, Investor Relations and Communications at 281-675-9107.
